Subject: Re: [T2] respirator for sandblasting?

Regarding silicosis- I was talking to a professional sandblaster last night,
and asked him about this issue. He said they haven't used silicate sand for
years because of the dangers involved. They use different sand even though
it isn't as effective a blasting media. And, they always use suits with
supplied air, even on their mobile units.

